snippet.title: Gta 5 Rare SuperCar Locations in Story Mode | Latest Build (PS4, XBox One, PC) 2022
snippet.description:
Rare Bikes Locations(Can't Buy):
▫️Dinka Double-T - https://bit.ly/36E0nww
▫️Shitzu Hakuchou - https://bit.ly/38fK8WO
▫️Principe Nemesis - https://bit.ly/3vhTpqN
▫️Dinka Thrust - https://bit.ly/3rLsp0i
▫️Western Daemon - https://bit.ly/3LbaiZr

Hey what's up you guys, im back with another tutorial on Gta V after many years later! So today I'm gonna show you how to find Super cars in Gta 5 Story Mode(offline) with the exact spawn locations and other random locations that you can find customised sport cars.

You'll find almost everything you need to know upto date because im playing on the one of the latest version which is 2372 build, 1.57 online (1.58 is the most recent one) and i can ensure that these locations and methods are working across most of the platforms including ps5, ps4, xbox one, xbox series x and pc(which im demonstrating). If you're a returning player on ps3 and xbox 360, you'll also be able to find these exotic vehicles.

This is what i found so far

SuperCars:
▫️Grotti Turismo R
▫️Pegassi Zentorno

Sports Cars(Customized):
▫️Pegassi Infernus
▫️Dinka Jester
▫️Benefactor Surano
▫️Bravado Gauntlet
▫️Coil Voltic

►Leaving a LIKE would always appreciate! 
►Subscribe for latest video uploads! http://bit.ly/29ZRld9

Our social media:
◽Like on Facebook: http://bit.ly/2acp9pO
◽Follow on Twitter: http://bit.ly/6zco6Xb
◽Message on Hangouts: Redux Dreams Lab

Notice:
◽If you find nothing at the parking slot, don't switch the characters yet. Just circulate around the blocks until you find a super car. 
◽Switch characters when you only found a super car
◽It's not necessary to go too far away from the parking lot in order to respawn vehicles. 
◽Random cars will be spawned while you drive around. They cannot be found parked in the shown locations. 

Thanks for watching and see you back!
